00050 static int rna_Main_is_dirty_get(PointerRNA *ptr)
00051 {
00052     /* XXX, not totally nice to do it this way, should store in main ? */
00053     Main *bmain = (Main*)ptr->data;
00054     wmWindowManager *wm;
00055     for (wm = bmain->wm.first; wm; wm = wm->id.next) {
00056         return !wm->file_saved;
00057     }
00058 
00059     return TRUE;
00060 }
